      <title>볼링공 대신 소방 호스로 ‘스트라이크’</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/10/31/IOH5RXVPZ5BCTBI63F2NXWWJBI/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/10/31/IOH5RXVPZ5BCTBI63F2NXWWJBI/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
